Title: See Mr. Peanutbutter Run
Writer: Raphael Bob-Waksberg (creator), Peter Knight, Alison Tafel (staff writer)
Actors: Will Arnett, Amy Sedaris, Alison Brie, Paul F. Tompkins
Plot: Mr. Peanutbutter starts his campaign for Governor of California by challenging the current governor to a ski race while BoJack is nowhere to be found.
